## 13. Combinações canônicas (pipelines)

### Pipeline 1 — Feature completa do zero ao deploy
```
/recall-learnings
  → /gsd-plan-phase (PLAN.md)
    → /gsd-execute-phase (waves)
      → /gsd-verify-work (VERIFICATION.md)
        → /code-review (current diff)
          → /lovable-handoff (typecheck → commit → push → handoff)
            → /extract-learnings (gate triplo)
```

### Pipeline 2 — Fix rápido em produção
```
/idea bug X
  → /gsd-quick
    → /lovable-handoff
      → /extract-learnings (se replicável)
```

### Pipeline 3 — Story formal (AIOX)
```
@pm *create-epic
  → @sm *draft (story)
    → @po *validate-story-draft
      → @dev *develop-story
        → @qa *qa-gate
          → @devops *push
```

### Pipeline 4 — Debugging de incidente
```
/recall-learnings
  → /gsd-debug
    → docs/postmortems/YYYY-MM-DD-<slug>.md
      → /extract-learnings (sempre — incidente é padrão)
        → atualizar AGENTS.md se necessário
```

